    "updated_at": "2015-01-02T20:20:42Z",
    "body": "There is no way to directly control the DOM of another window, you have to make use of `ipc` module to send messages to achieve that.\n\nIt works like this:\n1. The \"control\" window sends a \"draw xxx\" message to browser process\n2. The browser process redirects the \"draw xxx\" message to the \"canvas\" window\n3. The \"canvas\" window does the drawing when received \"draw xxx\" message\n"
